replies.body:
Hey Taz, the comment of yours removed was;

> I love this feminist theme on the boards right now, please don't stop :D

It was part of an inappropriate discussion in the thread which was off-topic and significantly distracting from the original post. While we don't really blame people for jumping in to comment on it, we had to remove every reply so that the topic at hand could be discussed. This is no strike against those people like yourself, it was merely cleanup and prevention of the inappropriate topic from continuing to derail the thread.
